Summary Calendar.*

United States Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Aug. 16, 1971. Max P. Engel, John A. Boecabella, Miami, Fla., for defendant-appellant. *652Robert W. Rust, U. S. Atty., William C. White, First Asst. U. S. Atty., Miami, Fla., for plaintiff-appellee.
